  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 8-10 Creation Points </p><p></p><p>You throw your BIM and it explodes in on impact making an audible and distinct cracking sound.</p><p> Make a ranged ninjutsu attack roll against a creature within the range you can throw B.I.Ms.</p><p> On a hit, the creature automatically fails the saving throw against this B.I.M.</p><p> Creatures within a 15-foot-radius sphere must make a Dexterity saving throw.</p><p> Dealing 3d8 lightning damage and gain 1 rank of Shocked on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p> Upgraded: For every 1 Creation Point after the minimum initial cost increase the damage dice by 1 or the ranks of Shocked by 1.</p><p></p>",
